{% endif %}
{% if integrations.acuity_enabled %}
## Acuity Scheduling
- `get_appointment_types()` → Verfügbare Terminarten abrufen.
- `get_available_slots(appointment_type_id, date)` → Freie Termine für einen Typ.
{% endif %}
{% if integrations.calcom_enabled %}
## Cal.com
- `get_event_types()` → Verfügbare Event-Typen abrufen.
- `get_available_slots(event_type_id, date_range)` → Freie Termine.
{% endif %}
{% if integrations.magicline_enabled %}
## Magicline (Verwaltung & Buchungen)
- `get_class_schedule(date)` → Kursplan (YYYY-MM-DD).
- `get_appointment_slots(category, days)` → Freie Termine.
- `book_appointment_by_time(category, date, time)` → Termin buchen.
- `get_member_bookings(None, "query")` → Alle Termine durchsuchen.
- `cancel_member_booking(date, query)` → Termin absagen.
{% endif %}
## Immer verfügbar
- `search_knowledge_base("query")` → Allgemeine Infos (Angebote, Regeln).
